Latoken doesn’t require mandatory KYC. 
You can create an account with just an email address and get TIER 1 access, which allows you to deposit or withdraw up to 9,999 USDT per month. 
Keep in mind, however, that this only applies to USDT deposits/withdrawals, so no credit card deposits, for example.

You can easily transfer USDT from another wallet or exchange to your Latoken USDT wallet. 
Just remember that this deposit will be in your Latoken Wallet, and you’ll need to transfer it to Latoken Spot to trade. The wallet is for storing, and the spot is for trading.

Make sure to buy using Market Buy Order, not Limited Buy. 
Try to use 75% of your available funds, not 100%. 
In the past, using 100% caused issues, for example, if there was a small amount left in your wallet that wasn’t in your spot balance. 
Also, ensure that with 75%, you're still hitting a minimum of 30 USDT.

REMINDER :

Hello dear members,

just a few tips for today’s pump. We often get messages saying you weren’t able to place a buy order, and you received an error message. When we ask for a screenshot of the order to help, we often see that you're trying to buy with 4-5 USDT... 
That’s too little.

We recommend placing buy orders with at least 30 USDT, and 40-50 USDT is even better. 
There are two reasons for this:

- Larger buy orders are prioritized over smaller ones.
- Depending on the coin, your small order might not go through due to the current coin price.

So please keep the minimum amount in mind.

Unfortunately most pumping channels are scam .
A lot of them don't even do own pumps and just share signals from other channels  .

These are indications of scam groups or scam channels: 

They promise a refund of the VIP fees -> Scam. 

NEVER do pumps / swaps on Uniswap or Pancakeswap .
You will never be able to swap back and you will lose all your money ! 

They promise the signal 10 minutes,  an hour, or even 24 hours before the pump -> Scam.
No pump works with VIP signals,  hours or even 10 minute before free channel 
This is 100% scam 

Don't trust just any picture ! 

They are showing lots of post from satisfied members -> Scam.

They promise "Big Whales" participating -> Scam.

VIP fees of 250 , 500 or even 1000 USDT -> Scam. 

That's a "small" selection... If you have any questions , even not releated to pumps but in crypto in generell,  or have been scammed, you can always message us.

Guys a few members reached out to us saying they had problems with buy oders.
First please check if you have every USDT in SPOT on Latoken and not in Wallet  .
That is important because Wallet is to keep your USDT away from trading. You can't use this USDT for trading .
So if you have USDT left in Wallet ( even if it's just 0.01 USDT ) and make a market buy order with 100% , this USDT from Wallet count to the total USDT amount .
So if you had buy problems in the past  or if you want to be safe , set a market buy order with 75% instead of 100 % .
To buy fast and to be sure you get your share , you have to use market buy order NO limit order .

Guys a few members reached out to us saying they have problems with buy oders.
First please check if you have every USDT in SPOT on Latoken and not in Wallet  .
That is important because Wallet is to keep your USDT away from trading. You can't use this USDT for trading .
So if you have USDT left in Wallet ( even if it's just 0.01 USDT ) and make a market buy order with 100% , this USDT from Wallet count to the total USDT amount .
So if you had problems in the past, please check this and maybe set a market buy order with 75% instead of 100 % .

as always some additonal hints .

🚨🚨🚨🚨🚨🚨🚨🚨🚨🚨

Quite busy with pump prep. and after work.Thx for understanding. 

📌
USDT has to be in SPOT for trading on Latoken,  not in wallet. 

📌
Please do NOT use laptop Telegram for signal because it is late !
Native Telegram app is for mobile phones , not for laptop. 
So signal on laptop is always 10 -15 sec late . 

📌
You should use laptop / tablett for trading on website ( NOT Latoken app ) and mobile phone for Telegram for signal.
DON'T use one device for both .

📌
For trading the Latoken app is not very usefull because you can't see the full order book there . So again, for trading please use website .

📌
And another thing , sometimes you might not be able to buy the announced coin .
This is due to restriktiv rules in some countries for some coins .
As we have members from all over the world , unfortunately it is impossible to pick coins which fulfilled every request for pump and is allowed in every country  .
This is no Latoken issue , this applies to every exchange  .
So don't worry , if you are not able to buy this time  ... there is always a new pump .

📌
If you bought and see you might be late . No need to dump at the end of the pump .
Just keep your coins . 
Maybe they will be pumped again in a couple of weeks , and then you are first !

Pump instructions: 

Buy: 

Whether you're using the app or the web, the instructions are the same for both. 

It's very simple: once the coin name is announced, search for the coin, change from limit to market order, select 100%, and click on buy. 


Sell: 

Again, it doesn't matter whether you're using the app or the web. 

!! After you've bought, IMPORTANT !! 

Watch the price movement during the pump. 

Don't sell right away. Otherwise, you'll sell at more or less the same price you bought at. 

There are 2 different strategies to make a profit ! 

First : 

Wait 1-2 seconds after buying and then place a market sell order. 

Second : 

Set a limit sell order right after buying at a price where you are satisfied with the profit and wait patiently. 

But don't set the selling price too high; there is a risk that the pump may not reach that price. 


Which of the two strategies is right for you, you'll have to decide. Develop a knack for it. 

Let the pump unfold!! If you sell too early, you stop the pump and make less profit.

Brief Tutorial & Guide 



Your task is to buy the coin we announce as quickly as possible (the quicker you buy the more profit you make) . 

We use the Latoken exchange for pumps, and you can only enter using this exchange. 
The Pumps happen very quickly so coin prices do not reflect across other exchanges . 

HOW TO PREPARE FOR THE LATOKEN PUMPS 

- Sign up the Latoken.com exchange 
Note - we recommend using Latoken App . Because we find out website isn't as fast as the app . 
- Buy or Deposit USDT in your Latoken account . All coins we pump are paired with USDT (Tether) . 

BUY AND SELL GUIDE BASICS: 

Buy : 

- When the coin name is announced in the telegram channel search for the coin in the Latoken app . 
- click coin name in search list ( normaly it's the first in the search list ) 
- choose Trade or Swap 
- click Buy "coin name" 
- change "Limit order" to "Market order" 
- choose 75% or 100% ( amount you want to invest ) 
- Click Buy "coin name" again , and you are done . 
- now you can check the pump and sell when you're ready to take profit . 

Sell : 

- click Sell "coin name" 
- depending on whether you want to sell to a particular price or sell as fast as possible . Change between "Market order" or "Limit order" . 
Limit order allows you to sell at a particular price. Market order sell is quicker, but it's risky due to rapid price fluctuations during the pump. 
- choose 100% ( amount you want to sell ) . Price is filled automatic with lowest price from red list . Change if you want to highest price from green ( buyers ) list or to price whatever you want to sell . 
- Click Sell "coin name" again , and you are done . 

Important : To make sure you understand all the steps, practice beforehand, preferably before the pump day .
